title: Somehow, My Country was destroyed, It isn’t my fault, right? ~Reincarnated Former Duke’s Daughter’s Dream of Happiness~ - Novel Updates
genre: Action   Adventure   Comedy   Fantasy   Gender Bender
tags: Cheats   Clever Protagonist   Dragon Slayers   Fearless Protagonist   Female Protagonist   Magic   Male to Female   Nobles   Overpowered Protagonist   Protagonist Strong from the Start   Reincarnated in Another World   World Travel
author: Poizun   ぽいずん
description:
A daughter of a duke who has regained memories of her previous life, and is engaged to be engaged to the crown prince!

No, I was a man in a previous life, so of course it’s impossible for me to marry a man.　

And so… come on! You have to break off the engagement!　　

The story of Alicia, the beloved child of the god of creation, who possesses immense magical power and is loved by the god of creation, wanders around, abandoning her country and her family to pursue her own happiness.

For that reason, even a dragon would be defeated.>
